title: Kris Jenner says Caitlyn Jenner can go f**k herself in Keeping Up With The Kardashians - US TV
text: Kris Jenner pulled no punches as she ranted about Caitlyn Jenner during yesterday's (October 4) episode of Keeping Up With The Kardashians.In a phone call with her daughter Kim, Kris made her feelings about Caitlyn's Vanity Fair cover interview very clear. Â© E!Caitlyn Jenner and Kris Jenner in I Am Cait finale "It just sums up that I'm this piece of shit person who was mean," she noted. "He can go f**k himself. I honestly wish I never met this man."Kim had visited Caitlyn during her Vanity Fair photo shoot and later confronted Caitlyn, but wasn't impressed by her lack of apology."You said, 'Oh, Kris mistreated me'. It sounded like she beat the shit out of you. You could have had a little bit more respect," Kim said.Keeping Up With The Kardashians airs on E!
